item.title: umm yea.. i should eat..
item.description: So yesterday I was really busy at work.. and I didn’t get a chance to eat lunch.. and of course.. I didn’t eat breakfast… and then I came home.. and just snacked and didn’t really get dinner. so today.. I am dieing.. everytime I stand up - everything starts spinning. haha.. silly head.. always blacking out. ;) it isn’t actually that bad.. but I am really really hungry.i can’t WAIT for lunch.
